Mehak..and I know it's not just paint.

668
01:13:40,370 --> 01:13:43,500
I swear if something jumps at me,
you better..

669
01:13:43,790 --> 01:13:44,950
Hey, what happened?

670
01:13:45,450 --> 01:13:47,950
I thought someone was
standing behind me. - Please.

671
01:13:48,370 --> 01:13:49,750
But I'm ok now.

672
01:13:51,250 --> 01:13:53,870
See this, the cement is still wet.

673
01:13:54,120 --> 01:13:55,500
