What the hell happened!
Where were you?

786
01:21:25,080 --> 01:21:26,200
Relax, mom!

787
01:21:26,330 --> 01:21:28,870
There was a whole nest
of spiders under Manu's bed.

788
01:21:29,160 --> 01:21:30,120
So I panicked.

789
01:21:30,540 --> 01:21:32,540
