790
01:21:33,250 --> 01:21:35,250
Anyway, look what I found.

791
01:21:37,410 --> 01:21:38,580
Unbelievable!

792
01:21:39,200 --> 01:21:40,250
Wow!

793
01:21:41,120 --> 01:21:42,500
Even I have this.

794
01:21:43,660 --> 01:21:44,660
Does that make me a murderer too?

795
01:21:44,750 --> 01:21:45,580
Maybe.

796
01:21:45,660 --> 01:21:49,200
Mehak, I told you to please
tell this girl to leave.

797
01:21:49,410 --> 01:21:51,540
Listen, Mehak can have
friends other than you as well.

798
01:21:51,620 --> 01:21:52,620
Stop getting so J.

799
01:21:52,700 --> 01:21:54,620
Do you want to put
this girl in trouble again?

800
01:21:54,870 --> 01:21:57,200
If you suffer a panic attack,
what will she do?

801
01:21:57,330 --> 01:21:59,620
Listen, you don't
need to worry about me.

802
01:21:59,700 --> 01:22:01,580
I can take care of myself.
I'm a black belt. - Right.

803
01:22:01,660 --> 01:22:03,450
And Mehak can never harm me.

804
01:22:03,500 --> 01:22:05,950
What if Malhotra files
a police complaint against you?

805
