You broke into his house.

806
01:22:07,330 --> 01:22:09,450
He won't do that, he's guilty.

807
01:22:09,500 --> 01:22:12,120
Oh Mehak, please! This is madness.

808
01:22:12,540 --> 01:22:14,160
Why aren't you helping us?

809
