Now Jiya will help us out.

810
01:22:18,750 --> 01:22:19,870
What?!

811
01:22:21,330 --> 01:22:24,830
Ok, it's written here that
to get in touch with the dead.

812
01:22:25,160 --> 01:22:29,540
To make contact, you've to
be in the same place where she died.

813
01:22:30,080 --> 01:22:31,080
Check.

814
01:22:31,700 --> 01:22:33,500
And it's written that you need..

815
01:22:33,580 --> 01:22:35,700
..to be in possession of
something that belonged to her.

816
01:22:36,120 --> 01:22:38,410
We have Jiya's clothes. Check.

817
01:22:40,120 --> 01:22:42,040
