No Nikki, that's Jiya. Can't you tell?

821
01:22:55,870 --> 01:22:56,830
Sorry.

822
01:23:08,200 --> 01:23:12,620
Jiya, we come in peace.
We mean no harm.

823
01:23:13,540 --> 01:23:16,580
We're here to listen
and help you move on.

824
01:23:16,660 --> 01:23:21,330
Jiya, we come in peace.
We mean no harm.

825
01:23:22,910 --> 01:23:24,830
Please talk to us.

826
