827
01:23:31,450 --> 01:23:33,830
That's because your
energy is very negative.

828
01:23:33,910 --> 01:23:35,160
Sure, its always my fault..

829
01:23:35,870 --> 01:23:36,950
Please keep quiet.

830
01:23:38,160 --> 01:23:39,500
We'll try again.

831
01:23:43,660 --> 01:23:45,410
Jiya, please talk to me.

832
01:23:46,790 --> 01:23:49,080
What happened to you in this house?

833
01:23:50,790 --> 01:23:53,040
We're here to help you.
Please talk to us

834
01:23:55,370 --> 01:23:56,250
Where are you..

835
01:24:39,830 --> 01:24:40,950
What the hell!

836
01:24:42,830 --> 01:24:45,830
Jiya tell us who killed you?
- What nonsense! Who are you people?

837
01:24:47,120 --> 01:24:48,750
What's all this?
Have you all gone mad?

838
01:24:48,830 --> 01:24:49,830
You're alive?

839
