- Sorry.. I'm Shaan, I can explain.

843
01:25:01,410 --> 01:25:02,830
Please explain, Shaan.

844
01:25:04,540 --> 01:25:07,160
Actually, I can't explain but..

845
01:25:07,250 --> 01:25:08,370
What?

846
01:25:11,410 --> 01:25:12,750
Did you call up my parents?

847
01:25:13,580 --> 01:25:15,500
Huh! Are you mad?

848
01:25:16,450 --> 01:25:19,450
Do you know how troubled my parents
were after hearing your message?

849
01:25:20,700 --> 01:25:22,120
Who does such a thing!

850
01:25:22,200 --> 01:25:25,250
'I know who killed your
daughter.' Manu made you say that?

851
01:25:25,370 --> 01:25:27,120
No, We thought Manu murdered you.

852
01:25:27,200 --> 01:25:30,450
I've overheard your fights.. - Shut up,
you nosey rat! I'm gonna kill Manu!

853
01:25:51,450 --> 01:25:54,120
Jiya, you're back! - Get off me!
Stay away from me, you sicko!

854
01:25:54,200 --> 01:25:55,750
Don't you understand it's over?

855
01:25:55,830 --> 01:25:57,910
I don't want your
grandma's rotten ring!

856
01:25:58,660 --> 01:26:00,040
Stay away or I'll
call the cops. - Jiya..

857
01:26:00,120 --> 01:26:01,910
Jiya, it's for you. - I don't want it.

858
01:26:01,950 --> 01:26:03,450
What did you tell them about us?

859
01:26:03,540 --> 01:26:04,870
Don't listen to them.

860
01:26:05,080 --> 01:26:06,870
They're all mental.
I love you.

861
01:26:06,950 --> 01:26:07,870
No, you don't. - Please come back.

862
01:26:07,950 --> 01:26:09,160
You hit me. – I'm sorry.

863
01:26:09,450 --> 01:26:10,790
Please calm down. - No, I won't.

864
01:26:10,870 --> 01:26:12,910
Sorry, I shouldn't have hit you.

865
01:26:12,950 --> 01:26:14,410
