866
01:26:14,450 --> 01:26:17,200
You know, I've done an advanced
course in laughter therapy.

867
01:26:18,790 --> 01:26:19,620
Shut up!

868
01:26:19,790 --> 01:26:22,200
I don't get angry anymore, see.
- Shut up!

869
01:26:23,750 --> 01:26:26,660
What do you want?
You want to continue flying?

870
01:26:26,750 --> 01:26:29,540
No problem. You don't
want to marry me? No problem.

871
01:26:29,790 --> 01:26:31,450
You don't want kids? No problem.

872
01:26:31,790 --> 01:26:33,620
You want to work with other guys?

873
01:26:34,700 --> 01:26:35,950
No problem.

874
01:26:36,160 --> 01:26:38,200
You don't want this ring now? Ok.

875
01:26:38,450 --> 01:26:41,080
I'll put it in my pocket.
I'll try later.

876
01:26:41,700 --> 01:26:44,410
I love you, baby.
Just come back.

877
01:26:44,450 --> 01:26:46,580
Get off! What are you doing?

878
01:26:46,660 --> 01:26:48,660
Please.. please, I'm sorry.

879
01:26:48,750 --> 01:26:51,250
I won't be stupid again.
Come back, please.

880
01:26:51,500 --> 01:26:52,910
I hate you.

881
01:26:53,080 --> 01:26:53,950
I know.

882
01:27:01,450 --> 01:27:03,620
If you laugh again, I'll slap you.
- I won't laugh.

883
01:27:14,870 --> 01:27:18,330
I have seen her in
the bathroom, Shaan.

884
01:27:19,580 --> 01:27:20,620
In the bedroom.

885
01:27:22,080 --> 01:27:23,120
All over the house.

886
01:27:24,160 --> 01:27:25,450
But she's alive.

887
01:27:27,750 --> 01:27:28,950
Why don't you say something?

888
01:27:29,120 --> 01:27:30,500
Mehak, I believe in you.

889
01:27:30,580 --> 01:27:32,250
There's definitely something
wrong with this house.

890
01:27:32,370 --> 01:27:34,200
Maybe it wasn't runaway Jiya but..

891
01:27:34,330 --> 01:27:36,700
..how do we now communicate
with the real ghost?

892
01:27:36,790 --> 01:27:40,330
We don't even have their clothes.
- Go home, Nikki. That's enough!

893
01:27:42,450 --> 01:27:43,410
Go home.

894
01:27:45,620 --> 01:27:46,870
And thank you for everything.

895
01:27:46,950 --> 01:27:48,200
Hey, what thank you?

896
01:27:48,450 --> 01:27:50,370
Say that when we catch the ghost.

897
01:27:50,620 --> 01:27:51,700
Happy Diwali.

898
01:28:00,660 --> 01:28:02,830
Are you going to send me
to mental hospital now?

899
01:28:04,450 --> 01:28:05,330
What?!

900
01:28:06,410 --> 01:28:07,580
No, M, never.

901
01:28:12,790 --> 01:28:17,120
I've never seen a more stronger
girl than you all my life.

902
01:28:19,120 --> 01:28:22,540
You will be fine,
I promise, just don't give up.

903
01:28:30,450 --> 01:28:31,790
Reality or imagination..

904
01:28:32,580 --> 01:28:35,950
Right or wrong,
I can't tell difference.

905
01:28:38,370 --> 01:28:39,620
I'm crazy.

906
01:28:41,040 --> 01:28:43,250
Please go.
- I'm not going anywhere, Mehak.

907
01:28:44,450 --> 01:28:45,500
I love you.

908
01:28:46,790 --> 01:28:48,120
I've always loved you.

909
01:28:53,500 --> 01:28:56,080
I'm so sorry.

910
01:29:34,500 --> 01:29:36,410
I hate your hands.

911
01:29:39,370 --> 01:29:41,830
Your touch disgusts me.

912
01:29:44,330 --> 01:29:46,040
Your hands are dirty..

913
01:29:53,830 --> 01:29:55,290
..ugly

914
01:30:02,790 --> 01:30:04,500
You've lost your mind.

915
01:30:06,910 --> 01:30:07,870
Not me.

916
01:30:11,160 --> 01:30:12,830
You need treatment, not me.

917
01:30:17,250 --> 01:30:18,410
Scoundrel..

918
01:30:19,750 --> 01:30:22,160
How dare you stare at me! - M?

919
01:30:23,200 --> 01:30:28,540
Who gave you the right to touch me?

920
01:30:30,500 --> 01:30:32,250
It's you who stinks

921
01:30:43,410 --> 01:30:45,200
Because you're rotten.

922
01:30:46,950 --> 01:30:50,410
I'm not wrong, you are.

923
01:30:52,080 --> 01:30:53,330
Wicked.

924
01:30:54,500 --> 01:30:57,790
Evil. Filthy.

925
01:31:02,410 --> 01:31:03,540
Sick.

926
01:31:06,200 --> 01:31:07,040
Why did you do it?

927
01:31:07,750 --> 01:31:09,080
What did you gain?
- Will you stop it?

928
01:31:09,160 --> 01:31:12,160
Do you know whom you're talking to?
- I'm talking to you, Shaan.

929
01:31:12,250 --> 01:31:15,200
You just don't understand me!

930
01:31:17,700 --> 01:31:20,450
You tell me to be brave.

931
01:31:21,450 --> 01:31:23,500
Go out. Go where?

932
01:31:24,910 --> 01:31:28,540
You told me, I wasn't raped.

933
01:31:30,200 --> 01:31:32,500
Should I have been raped?- Enough!

934
01:31:33,540 --> 01:31:36,540
If you touch me again,
I'll call the cops.

935
01:31:36,620 --> 01:31:39,450
Go ahead, call them over.
- You are Disgusting!

936
01:31:39,540 --> 01:31:41,750
The more people see this drama,
the better it will be

937
01:31:42,330 --> 01:31:45,410
I took you as my friend and what did
you do the moment you got a chance!

938
01:31:45,750 --> 01:31:47,330
How are you any different from him?

939
01:31:47,620 --> 01:31:49,120
How dare you say that!

940
01:31:49,200 --> 01:31:50,200
What about all the
stress you've been..

941
01:31:50,330 --> 01:31:51,450
..putting me through
over the past three years?

942
01:31:51,540 --> 01:31:53,500
We're friends today, lovers tomorrow,
who knows what we are the day after!

943
01:31:53,580 --> 01:31:55,080
Make up your bloody mind!

944
01:31:56,250 --> 01:31:58,160
I've done so much for you.

945
01:31:58,250 --> 01:31:59,450
I'm going to call Anu.

946
01:31:59,540 --> 01:32:01,450
I'm talking to you, you freak.

947
01:32:02,830 --> 01:32:05,040
M.. M..

948
01:32:05,370 --> 01:32:08,450
M, please.. that's enough!

949
01:32:27,870 --> 01:32:28,910
Oh god!

950
01:32:29,790 --> 01:32:31,250
M..

951
01:32:34,660 --> 01:32:37,160
I'm sorry, M. Are you hurt?
Let me check

952
01:32:37,250 --> 01:32:39,250
Stop it. - Help!

953
01:32:39,370 --> 01:32:40,450
Get away from me!

954
01:32:42,330 --> 01:32:43,410
M..

955
01:32:43,700 --> 01:32:44,700
Oh my god!

956
01:32:47,160 --> 01:32:48,330
Oh my god!

957
01:32:51,830 --> 01:32:53,500
Stay away from me!

958
01:32:53,580 --> 01:32:56,120
I'm not mad, you'll kill me.

959
01:32:56,450 --> 01:32:58,620
It wasn't Jiya, it was me. I was
seeing myself. I won't let you kill me.

960
01:32:58,700 --> 01:32:59,830
What are you saying, Mehak?

961
01:32:59,910 --> 01:33:01,870
Drop that blade,
you'll hurt yourself.

962
01:33:01,950 --> 01:33:03,580
I saw all of this!

963
