Drop the blade, M!

964
01:33:09,370 --> 01:33:12,080
No. - M, drop the blade.

965
01:33:31,870 --> 01:33:32,910
Look at me.

966
01:33:45,950 --> 01:33:47,450
Look at me.

967
01:33:48,120 --> 01:33:51,580
M, I'm going to take you
to the hospital. Look at me.

968
01:33:52,750 --> 01:33:54,580
M..

969
01:34:01,790 --> 01:34:02,790
Let's..

970
01:34:03,950 --> 01:34:05,040
The ice box..

971
01:34:07,330 --> 01:34:09,750
I'll be right back..wait..

972
01:35:49,410 --> 01:35:51,950
Hi, Mehak was..
- Nikki, do you know what time it is?

973
01:35:52,040 --> 01:35:54,750
I know, sorry but I got a
call from Mehak. - She's sleeping.

974
01:35:54,830 --> 01:35:57,660
I just thought it's something urgent.

975
01:35:57,750 --> 01:36:00,370
It's alright, she's sleeping.
I'm here, go home.

976
01:36:00,790 --> 01:36:02,790
Just tell her..

977
01:36:03,200 --> 01:36:04,450
What was that?

978
01:36:06,250 --> 01:36:08,790
Maybe the cat entered.

979
01:36:09,750 --> 01:36:12,450
Cat? Gul aunty's cat is back?

980
01:36:12,540 --> 01:36:14,040
She keeps coming
in through the window.

981
01:36:14,120 --> 01:36:15,660
Yes, I have to go now..

982
01:36:19,700 --> 01:36:20,580
Nikki, go home.

983
01:36:20,660 --> 01:36:21,620
What's that? - Over here.

984
01:36:21,700 --> 01:36:22,870
What? – On your...

985
01:36:22,950 --> 01:36:24,120
It's nothing, Nikki. Go home.

986
01:36:24,540 --> 01:36:26,870
No, I have to meet Mehak. - I'm
telling you she's sleeping. Go home.

987
01:36:26,950 --> 01:36:28,410
I don't believe you, Shaan.

988
01:36:28,450 --> 01:36:29,370
What do you mean
you don't believe me?

989
01:36:29,450 --> 01:36:31,750
She's sleeping, I can't wake her up.
- I'm not going.

990
01:36:31,830 --> 01:36:33,250
If she's sleeping, wake her up.
- Just relax.

991
01:36:33,370 --> 01:36:34,540
Nikki.. - I won't leave
without meeting her.

992
01:36:34,620 --> 01:36:36,330
Have you lost it?
Don't you understand?

993
01:36:36,410 --> 01:36:38,830
Nikki, get out.
- Not without meeting..

994
01:36:40,370 --> 01:36:41,750
Mehak! - Nikki!

995
01:36:48,540 --> 01:36:50,870
What have you done?
- I haven't done anything, Nikki.

996
01:36:51,040 --> 01:36:52,950
