997
01:36:53,040 --> 01:36:54,540
I swear, Nikki. I'm not lying.

998
01:36:54,620 --> 01:36:56,200
It was an accident, I swear.

999
01:36:56,330 --> 01:36:58,370
Mehak, I'm calling my dad.

1000
01:36:58,830 --> 01:37:00,500
Everything will be fine.

1001
01:37:02,040 --> 01:37:04,120
Nikki, listen to me. - No.

1002
01:37:04,370 --> 01:37:05,750
It was an accident, I swear. - No.

1003
01:37:05,830 --> 01:37:07,080
No! – Give me the phone.

1004
01:37:07,160 --> 01:37:09,620
Give me the phone! Let go! - No!

1005
01:37:10,620 --> 01:37:13,200
Leave it! Let me call the ambulance.

1006
01:37:20,370 --> 01:37:22,330
Stop it!

1007
01:37:26,580 --> 01:37:29,160
No, no.. Nikki.. Nikki!

1008
01:37:29,660 --> 01:37:32,540
Nikki, wake up!

1009
01:37:32,790 --> 01:37:34,950
Mehak, she's alive.
We need to take her to the hospital.

1010
01:37:35,500 --> 01:37:36,450
Mehak?

1011
01:37:37,950 --> 01:37:39,040
Mehak?

1012
01:37:53,160 --> 01:37:54,120
Mehak..

1013
01:38:45,620 --> 01:38:47,040
Mehak! Hey!

1014
01:38:48,330 --> 01:38:49,660
Mehak, open the door.

1015
01:38:50,450 --> 01:38:52,120
Mehak, open the door.

1016
01:38:54,580 --> 01:38:56,540
Mehak, open the door.
What are you doing?!

1017
01:38:56,910 --> 01:38:58,700
Why are you afraid of me, Mehak?

1018
01:39:00,750 --> 01:39:02,200
Why are you running away from me?

1019
01:39:03,790 --> 01:39:05,410
Your fight is not with me, Mehak.

1020
01:39:06,450 --> 01:39:07,660
It's with your self.

1021
01:39:09,750 --> 01:39:11,750
I know you're
standing outside, Mehak.

1022
01:39:16,410 --> 01:39:17,870
I won't do anything now.

1023
01:39:20,120 --> 01:39:21,540
I'm tired.

1024
01:39:23,450 --> 01:39:25,370
I'm so tired.

1025
01:39:42,160 --> 01:39:43,830
You need to get to
the hospital, princess.

1026
01:39:48,330 --> 01:39:49,870
And your finger's in the freezer.

1027
01:40:04,410 --> 01:40:08,410
Ma'am, I'm calling from B-603,
Overlook Apartments.

1028
01:40:08,450 --> 01:40:09,500
Malad East.

1029
01:40:10,750 --> 01:40:12,910
I need an ambulance,
it's a medical emergency.
